            %li.normal-list 3. Take 2-4 photos and measurements of your room
            %li.normal-list 4. Gather any inspiration links or pictures. 
            %li.normal-list 
              5. Send this all to us via email 
              %a.normal-link{:href => "mailto:bridget@chirigosdesigns.com"} (bridget@chirigosdesigns.com)
          %h2 What do you receive?
          %p Depending on the scope of your project, your personalized Design Plan may include:
          %ul.normal-list
