            %li.normal-list &diams; Ideas for items to reuse and/or revamp
            %li.normal-list &diams; List and links to all resources to complete the project.
          %h2 How long does it take to receive your personalized Design Plan?
          %p Once we received your questionnaire, photos, measurements, inspiration links and your payment, we begin the design process.  
          %ul.normal-list
            %li.normal-list 
              %b &diams; Silver Package: 
              2 business days or less 
            %li.normal-list 
              %b &diams; Gold Package: 
              1 to 2 weeks
            %li.normal-list 
              %b &diams; Diamond Package: 
              3-4 weeks
          %h2 Payment Options
          %p Have more questions or require more time? We charge an additional $30/hour for phone calls, emails and additional research.
          %p Payment is due in full when the client questionnaire, room photos and inspiration links have been submitted. We accept Paypal, check or money order. All designs are non refundable.
